    ALT: 18,
    ESC: 27,
    SPACE: 32,
    END: 35,
    HOME: 36,
    LEFT: 37,
    UP: 38,
    RIGHT: 39,
    DOWN: 40,
    PAGE_UP: 33,
    PAGE_DOWN: 34,

    // version 0.x

    LEFT_ARROW: 37,
    UP_ARROW: 38,
